{"tid":190754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣最美的是人】台的士司機醉駕撞死高中生，穿紅衣闖靈堂","createTime":"2017-04-07T10:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T10:30:42.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4541b080ea927a0884e69779725bcf803c9e3d6b","tid":190754,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"台灣花蓮市一名黃姓高二男學生（18歲），&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;上月30日騎單車赴校參加考試時，途中遭醉駕的士司機蘇宏銘（34歲）撞死。<br />\n<br />\n在黃男告別儀式的前一天，涉事司機竟穿着鮮紅色T恤、脖子繫紅繩到殯儀館拜祭死者。<br />\n<br />\n家屬見狀喝斥：「撞死人穿這樣對嗎？」蘇竟回答：「你那隻眼睛看見我撞他？」家屬今日接受台《蘋果》訪問，並展示蘇男穿紅衣去殯儀館照片。"},{"pid":"d4c657375c07ae7a88aa84c63e5106e785fc2549","tid":190754,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491549640_fc93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491549640_fc93.jpg&h=786a93b7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}